{"tid":2123971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"35%非黃絲：入境檢疫失策","createTime":"2020-07-25T05:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T05:49:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"486c454a420bd322f88496fb8ee964174cb0384c","tid":2123971,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/45UCGMLHPKWB5KT35C7C6CRX6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2F45UCGMLHPKWB5KT35C7C6CRX6E%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=e00fff5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2F45UCGMLHPKWB5KT35C7C6CRX6E%2F&h=e989f0b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/45UCGMLHPKWB5KT35C7C6CRX6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n35%非黃絲：入境檢疫失策<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vvvh8mkNN8QpmKeSCcpszTZ_GLI=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MP5G64Z3ID3XZ62ECGZ5BDLO5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fvvvh8mkNN8QpmKeSCcpszTZ_GLI%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMP5G64Z3ID3XZ62ECGZ5BDLO5E.jpg&h=4b934c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港民研調查發現，港人對第三波疫情的警覺乃至憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【香港民研調查】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港疫情日趨嚴重，政府被批未有做好把關工作引致疫情反彈。香港民意研究所調查發現，近35%支持非民主派的受訪者，認同近期疫情爆發，是港府入境檢疫政策失誤所致，民主派支持者的認同比率更高達97%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三成市民預計自己染疫<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：入境處工會主席三消防中招<br />\n<br />\n香港民研本月16日至23日訪問逾9,000名市民，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n調查亦詢問受訪者對港府應對疫情的表現，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：政府公佈25檢疫酒店 柏寧上榜<br />\n<br />\n香港民研另一個調查亦訪問近9,000名來自不同政治光譜的市民，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n結果發現，941名自稱非民主派支持者中，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n公共衞生研究社召集人陳盈指調查結果顯示即使持不同政見的港人，均認為港府在豁免部份入境人士檢疫的措施，是導致第三波疫情爆發的主因。她又引述港大醫學院院長梁卓偉日前的說法，指第三波疫情確診者體內病毒基因與第二波疫情不同，相信病毒源頭來自境外輸入個案。"},{"pid":"2ed0bdec050afe1c7886cbb1297be383b4cf94c0","tid":2123971,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"林鄭死哂香港人都唔會封<br />\n封關即係嗰時醫護罷工岩自己睇錯<br />\n佢之後仲要搞清算，點會認輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86d25b4846a2ac0bcbda69aaadf7709d7d03f6d","tid":2123971,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"即係仲有65%智力有問題垃圾覺得疫情係黃中絲初選...."},{"pid":"4049625497857cc0fef517720f19ea1edccaf8f0","tid":2123971,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:39:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2af34962e4f2e47e0fc932f3f7bc9190f95740b4","tid":2123971,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"社會上就存在好多<br />\n唔支持警察 屌政府 丶但係覺得抗爭係搞亂 丶投票又偏建制。亦唔會特別支持咩黃藍 ，好食好買黃藍都會幫襯<br />\n呢堆簡稱為港豬"},{"pid":"0a5ede277d3e2b9e4e0139647b54eb03ecc1874c","tid":2123971,"uid":247892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2af34962e4f2e47e0fc932f3f7bc9190f95740b4","tid":2123971,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"社會上就存在好多<br />\n唔支持警察 屌政府 丶但係覺得抗爭係搞亂 丶投票又偏建制。亦唔會特別支持咩黃藍 ，好食好買黃藍都會幫襯<br />\n呢堆簡稱為港豬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"事實<br />\n佢地生活係香港係要奶盡著數<br />\n佢地唔鍾意原有生活環境受影響<br />\n你同佢地講咩理想簡直bull shit<br />\n乜野黑白是良知都係廢話"}]}